      <code>apply_latest_to_reliability</code>.</li>
  <li><b>Ground-truth labelling effort</b> &mdash; not a dev task; reviewers need to populate
      <code>calibration_labels</code>. Nightly Celery refit picks them up automatically.</li>
</ul>

<h3>8.7 Phase 6 &mdash; Robustness &amp; continuous monitoring (live + remediations)</h3>
<ul>
  <li><b>Per-deployment threshold calibration</b> for KL drift (currently hard-coded constants).</li>
  <li><b>Hallucination detector hardening</b>: entity check via NER (not regex on capitalised n-grams);
      statistic check on numeric synthesis across the union of sources, not single-source membership.</li>
  <li><b>Numeric grounding</b> in <code>multi_llm_verifier.py</code> against <code>country_indicators</code> for
      emissions/renewable claims (closes the &ldquo;both LLMs agree on a hallucinated number&rdquo; failure mode).</li>
</ul>

<h3>8.8 Phase 7 &mdash; Agentic chat tool-use (proposed; not started)</h3>
<p>The single largest user-experience uplift identified in the UI/UX audit. Backend exposes an optional
<code>actions: [{type, params, label}]</code> payload on <code>/api/chat</code>; client renders clickable chips above
the message input. Minimum viable action types:</p>
<ul>
  <li><code>navigate</code>, <code>analyze_url</code>, <code>apply_search_filters</code>, <code>apply_map_filters</code>,
      <code>open_methodology_section</code>, <code>open_country</code>, <code>start_deep_search</code>,
      <code>bookmark_article</code>, <code>start_calibration_label</code> (admin).</li>
</ul>

<h3>8.9 Phase 8 &mdash; Production &amp; scale</h3>
<ul>
  <li><b>Cloud cut-over</b> on GCP project <code>climatenews-495412</code>, region <code>europe-west4</code>: in progress.
      Cloud Build config for the frontend image landed in commit <code>edb0a23</code>; backend Cloud Run service
      <code>climatenews-api</code> is live; frontend Cloud Run service <code>climatenews-frontend</code> at
      <code>https://climatenews-frontend-srzwxdzmaq-ez.a.run.app/</code>.</li>
  <li><b>Override <code>INGESTION_COUNTRIES</code></b> on Cloud Run API service with the 80-country global list
      (current default is 23 EU-leaning codes; root cause of the &ldquo;cloud only sees BG/RO/SI/ES&rdquo; symptom).</li>
  <li>Cloud Scheduler triggers for the 6 indicator adapters + 3 calibration refits (HTTP POST with
      <code>X-Scheduler-Secret</code> / <code>X-Admin-Secret</code>).</li>
  <li>HTTPS + CDN + monitoring (Grafana / Prometheus / Jaeger).</li>
  <li>Mobile app (React Native or PWA) &mdash; deferred.</li>
  <li>Real-time alerting for breaking climate events &mdash; deferred.</li>
</ul>

<h3>8.10 Phase 9 &mdash; Long-horizon (Video Production Pipeline)</h3>
<p>Per the original vision document, an end-to-end &ldquo;article &rarr; vertical video &rarr; social post&rdquo; pipeline
remains the longest-horizon target:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Script generation (Claude / DeepSeek) &rarr; TTS (ElevenLabs / Azure) &rarr; B-roll search (Pexels API) &rarr;
      fact-check graphic generation &rarr; FFmpeg / Remotion render (1080&times;1920, 9:16, 15&ndash;60s).</li>
  <li>Social media OAuth + publish API integrations: TikTok, Instagram Reels (Graph API), YouTube Shorts (Data API v3),
      LinkedIn, X.</li>
  <li>Scheduled auto-publish + analytics ingestion (views, likes, shares).</li>
</ul>
<p>Database schema sketches for <code>videos</code>, <code>social_media_posts</code>, <code>user_social_accounts</code>
already exist in the vision doc but are not yet provisioned.</p>

