<h3>9.2 Required environment variables (launch)</h3>
<ul>
  <li><b>Core:</b> <code>JWT_SECRET_KEY</code> (&ge;32 chars), <code>DATABASE_URL</code>, <code>REDIS_URL</code>.</li>
  <li><b>OAuth:</b> <code>GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID</code>, <code>GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET</code>, <code>OAUTH_STATE_SECRET</code>;
      optional <code>MICROSOFT_CLIENT_ID</code>, <code>MICROSOFT_CLIENT_SECRET</code>, <code>MICROSOFT_TENANT_ID</code>.</li>
  <li><b>Scheduler/admin:</b> <code>SCHEDULER_SECRET</code>, <code>CLILENS_CALIBRATION_ADMIN_SECRET</code>.</li>
  <li><b>LLM providers:</b> <code>DEEPSEEK_API_KEY</code>, <code>ANTHROPIC_API_KEY</code>, <code>ANTHROPIC_MODEL</code>,
      <code>OPENAI_API_KEY</code>; optional <code>PERPLEXITY_API_KEY</code>, <code>CARF_API_URL</code> + <code>CARF_API_KEY</code>.</li>
  <li><b>Ingestion:</b> <code>INGESTION_COUNTRIES</code> &mdash; <i>override with the 80-country global list on Cloud Run</i>.</li>
  <li><b>Enrichment:</b> <code>CLILENS_ENRICHMENT_PROVIDER</code> (deepseek|openai|anthropic|unset for cascade),
      <code>CLILENS_TRAINING_DATASET_PATH</code>.</li>
  <li><b>Frontend:</b> <code>NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL</code>, <code>NEXT_PUBLIC_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID</code>,
      <code>NEXT_PUBLIC_MICROSOFT_CLIENT_ID</code>.</li>
</ul>

